items.name: Tony Tony Chopper (One Piece)
items.description:
I am the Reindeer Czar, I love Reindeer and Wolves. Tony Tony Chopper is my favorite character from One Piece. Now you can include him in your SD install. The model is not perfect. Some models have confusion with a few details like his antlers and his hoof hands, but I think we have prompted to minimize the bad parts.

Even with this, you can still get some really cool images. We wanted to include more chopper transformations, but only Arm Point is there so far. That is a cool one. We tested it with a bunch of different models to give examples, look below!

You can invoke his Arm Point transformation, by including ArmPoint in your prompt. Other tags like (Big Muscles, Big Forearms, Big Biceps, Fists, Fingers), help too. You can also add a Rumble Ball to your prompt. Just add the tag, RumbleBall, you can add like (holding object, holding RumbleBall) to try and get him to hold it. Sometimes it works, sometimes not, but still cool.

Crying Chopper was also included, but we forgot about that until right now, so we have not tried to invoke the meme, but it should work. (Sad, Crying, Crying with eyes open) should be able to add to your image.

Weigh like 0.75 to 1.0 - I prompt typically like this:

His Basic Attributes:

(brown fur, short, animal ears, antlers, hooves, black eyes, snout)


What he is wearing:

(hat, pink headwear, shorts, full body) + Backpack too if you like.

What he is doing:

(outdoor, ship, deck, deckchair, porthole, ocean, pirate flag)

Negative Tags:

We highly recommend removing (loli, child) if you have in your negative tag, not for gross reasons, but because those tags make it more likely to make Chopper's body go off model. Also we recommend adding (extra antlers:1.6), (weird antlers:1.6), (extra ears:1.6) this will help his antlers not look quite as weird, and be closer to on model.

If you make some cool images please post them we'd love to see them!

items.name: The Electric Age - LORA (Electric Bastionland Style)
items.description:
Bastion, the electric hub of mankind. The only city that matters. Everything is here, everybody's here. People, aliens and mockeries, getting in your way and in your business.

You have a failed career, and a colossal debt. Treasure is your only hope.

Hey folks,

This LORA is made to emulate the style of the TRPG Electric Bastionland written by Chris McDowall and illustrated by Alec Sorenson. While my previous LORAs were released as alphas, my experience from optimizing those has allowed me to anticipate some issues and allow for faster testing. I'm pretty happy with the LORA so far, and I'm releasing the "beta2" version.

Some notes on using the model:

  • Weights seem to be very flexible. If you want to stick close to the original style, you can stay within the 0.8 to 1.0 range, but you can create interesting effects all the way down to 0.4

  • This model was trained on animefull/CLIP SKIP 2. I will be training a CLIP SKIP 1 version later as well. Still, I think the anime model environment is a good fit for this illustration style.

  • The emulated style is lo-fi and surreal by default, so you may need to use higher resolutions/high-res fix (as appropriate for your base model) and proper prompting/embeddings to guarantee clear faces and details.

  • For color, try different combinations of "monochrome" "greyscale" "spot color" and "limited palette" for different effects.

  • So far, testing has been limited to the Silicon29 models, as well as a bit of Counterfeit. More models will be testing before releasing the next version.

  • EDIT: If you want to generate mockeries, I'd recommend konyconi's MuppetManiaAI LORA for now. I will look into training the concept into the final version.

items.name: RunDiffusion FX Photorealistic
items.description:
RunDiffusion FX Photorealistic

RunDiffusion FX brings ease, versatility, and beautiful image generation to your doorstep.

Join us on our Discord: https://discord.com/invite/wH6dTyBpCf
RunDiffusion.com - Powerful Cloud Servers hosting Automatic1111, InvokeAi and other open source tools.

The RunDiffusion FX Model Series is a game-changer in the realm of image generation. Balancing simplicity and functionality, this model transforms your brief prompts into diverse, imaginative images. Its versatility caters to a spectrum of creative needs, from the novice enthusiast to the seasoned artist. Above all, it's the ability to produce striking outputs that truly sets it apart. See more image examples here.

How to use the model

We set out to create a model that can accept small prompts yet generate amazing results. We've done that with RunDiffusion FX. Watch our guide on YouTube.

  • Small prompts work great!

    (hyperrealism:1.2), BREAK fish swimming under the water BREAK (8K UHD:1.2), (photorealistic:1.2)

  • Use a Negative!

    e.g. Negative Prompt: plain background, boring, plain, standard, homogenous, uncreative, unattractive, opaque, grayscale, monochrome, distorted details, low details, grains, grainy, foggy, dark, blurry, portrait, oversaturated, low contrast, underexposed, overexposed, low-res, low quality, close-up, macro, surreal, multiple views, multiple angles

  • Wide/Tall aspect ratios are awesome!

    • Resolutions like 480x832 832x480 work great then you can upscale.

  • Lower that CFG! You can use a CFG scale of 3.5 to 5 to get some softer photorealistic images.

Olivio Sarikas Likes it!

We did not ask him to create this video. This was a surprise to us!

License

RunDiffusion supports collaboration and innovation, therefore we are releasing this model free and open for all to use. There are only a few simple rules we'd ask you to adhere to:

  • Always use the name of the model in any generation service.

    • "RunDiffusion FX - Photorealistic"

    • "RunDiffusion FX - 2.5D"

  • Do not change the name or obfuscate it.

  • Credit us in any merges

  • Do not resell the model itself

  • Enjoy

items.name: 🦊 Fox Model 🦊
items.description:
-Fox Model-

The swiss army knife for anime generations.

(works very well with loras as well.)

🧦 -Fox in Sox-🧦

(A high resolution model meant for upscaling to 1440p)

Basic setup:

Resolutions: 512x768 / 768x768 / (768x512 not thoroughly tested)

CFG Scale: (10-13)

Steps: Not accounting for Hires.Fix (50-90)

Recommended Sampling Methods: DPM++ 2m karras, DPM Adaptive, DPM++ 2M SDE karras

Vae: vae ft mse 84000

Clip Skip: 2

Notes:

  • None of the examples will be using Hires.fix and will all be Seed 1 and extremely short prompts.

  • I would recommend using SwinIR_4x for Hires. It may not be the best upscaler for everything however, it is a good all around choice for anything.

  • A very flexible model, mixing with some more realistic models can lead to some very decent results if you prefer to have a more realistic style.

  • Extremely long or confusing prompts can cause, the generation to come out with errors. Try to be straightforward when making your prompt - listing tags from most important, to least important.

  • This is an Alpha Model, I insist on others making mixes in order to improve results. Please leave feedback.

items.name: ShigureKira-Honkai 3rd-时雨绮罗
items.description:
中文

一次就成功了的时雨绮罗，效果是真的不错捏。头部还原的很好，换衣服也很容易。可惜的不对称的丝袜，小辫子和经典屁股披风没有学到~触发词为"ShigureKira",添加"hair ribbon,ponytail,armored dress,single legwear,white boots,detached sleeves,fingerless gloves,white scarf"来获得更好的输出。虽然有点长哈，但还原的确实不错。推荐权重0.8，换衣服适当降低权重到0.6，保留触发词和头部相关提示词。训练素材为纯黑背景，稍微添加点背景描述词防止出现纯黑色背景。如果她的衣领很牢固，请添加“collarbone”去除。

English

The ShigureKira model was completed in one go, and the effect is really good. The head is restored very well, and changing clothes is also very easy. It's a pity that the model didn't learn the asymmetrical stockings, braids and classic butt capes~ The trigger word is "ShigureKira", add "hair ribbon,ponytail,armored dress,single legwear,white boots,detached sleeves,fingerless gloves,white scarf" to for better output. items.name: LLAS style (Lovelive All Stars)
items.description:
本LORA模型是由LLAS手游的立绘图训练的，共计1500+张图，训练了20epoch。所有训练图片均为横*纵：1024*768

This LORA model was trained by over 1500 pics of mobile game of LLAS, with 20 epoch. All of those trained images were 1024*768.

该LORA的效果主要体现在能让画面的饱和度明显增加，将非常多光效、特效的效果体现出来。

This LORA have effects on increasing the saturation of the picture and reflecting a lot of light effects and special effects.

并且因为LLAS内的服饰非常华丽，使用此LORA在绘制裙子、卫衣、礼服等众多服饰的时候会变得更加华丽。

In addition, because the clothing of LLAS is very gorgeous, using this LORA will become more gorgeous when drawing skirts, hoodies, gowns, etc.

使用此LORA不需要添加trigger word，您可以开比较小的权重来让画面产生不同的效果。

There is no need to add a trigger word with this LORA, and you can use a small weight to give different effects to the image.

由于本人刚开始尝试制作画风LORA，因此多少会存在一些问题。由于训练集全为横向的图，在纵向生成的时候可能会出现一些肢体错误（尤其体现在手）由于LLAS画风比较强烈，其中眼睛的变化尤为明显，因此如果不希望产生太大的变化，您可以降低权重来使用，或者不要用此LORA绘制面部。以上问题我将会持续研究改进，如果有新的问题发现请务必提出，感谢您的支持。

As I just started making painting style LORA, so there will be some problems. Since the training set is all horizontal drawings, there may be some body errors (especially hands) during the vertical generation. As LLAS painting style is strong, the changes of eyes are particularly obvious. Therefore, if you do not want to have too much change, you can reduce the weight to use it, or do not use this LORA to draw the face. I will continue to study and improve the above problems. If you find any new problems, please be sure to raise them. Thank you for your support.

I don't think this model is perfect by any chance but it a decent one.
If you like the model please consider leaving a review.

Trained for 4 epoches but the forth one is overfit so decided to publish the 3rd Epoch.

I was going to fix the issues but since i'm too lazy to do it here are the known issues :

  • Her hoodie can be whacky sometime especially clothes manipulation such as windy effect or open clothes etc.

  • Her blue pants is not recognized very well resulting in blue jeans pants. (probably need more training for the lower half)

  • Can't produce fishnets really well. At least it's acceptable. So, Good Luck trying.

  • On her alternate hairstyle(side ponytail),can appear on both side. If that happen Keep generating. you'll eventually get the right one or the left XD.

This Lora Include 2 versions the Original Shippuden Outfit and the Alternate Hairstyle from the onsen Scene. Both versions can be used interchangeably.

Basic Prompt for Shippuden Outfit:
masterpiece, absurdres, 1girl, hinata\(shippuden\),solo,blush, hooded jacket, headband around neck, konohagakure symbol, fishnets, blue pants, looking at viewer, outdoors, sunlight,smile,cowboy shot
